result.formatted_address: 74 Hak Po St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Joyful Dessert House

reviews.text: I loved my dessert! It seemed thoughtfully made and presented, and was worth the wait. This place is often busy with a wait, especially on the weekends. But definitely worth a try.

The grilled pineapple and sorbet tasted really good. The space is tight and small. And there are often lines. As long as you don’t mind waiting the desserts are pretty good. The AC was on blast and a girl requested to have it turned down and the waitress was good about it.
Clearly only cheap ingredients were used. You could taste that cheap syrups, whipping cream and ice creams weee frequently used or served. Not quite worth the reputation. Quite disappointing.
Pineapple dessert very good. The pineapple slice with the sugar coating is just right. Pineapple crumble is hot and delicious. Strongly recommend to go to this restaurant if you like Pineapple!

Mediocore dessert on the pricey end. We were tempted by the Michellin recommendation and ordered their signature dish Matcha Lava Cake. Not much molten Matcha Lava and the cake is not hot when served. Apple crumble taste alright ($54) but it is too small for its price. Service non existence, waitress trying to clean our desk ASAP. Not sure why there is so many people waiting outside the store.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角黑布街74號
result.name: Joyful Dessert House

reviews.text: 忙果拿破侖超好食👍

食完飯，朋友們話想食甜品。係白布街黑布街，見門面幾靚，又貼住米芝連2019既貼紙，所以就一試喇。我叫左芒果拿破崙，朋友們就叫左燒菠蘿雪芭同芒果七色椰果芭菲。

芒果拿破崙賣相好靚，上既芒果好靚好新鮮，拿破崙好脆好好食，再加上一球芒果雪糕，食件事即刻好完美。

朋友點既芒果七色椰果芭菲，佢起初話睇落咁細杯既，但最終食好耐，同埋食完猛叫好正好飽🤣。

至於燒菠蘿雪芭，菠蘿好甜好正，雪芭都係，仲俾人一種好清新既感覺。

店既唯一缺點，可能係女性顧客比較多，相對地嘈左少少。

走在路上不小心撞到的"2017米其林街頭小食推薦"
店面的斜對角就是ㄧ間米其林輪胎店實在很令人多想=w=
當時吃過晚餐後想吃甜點的我們看排隊人不多我們就進去了
簡單的小店
非常友善的服務員
舒服的冷氣
在夏天的香港非常重要
而既然菜單上明顯地標出3款米其林推薦的甜點
也沒什麼好考慮的
就各來ㄧ份
細節依然放在照片中
是間很不錯有一點點驚訝的甜點店
若有到香港經過旺角的話可以來品嘗看看

閒日夜晚食完飯大概10:00過嚟
唔算等位等太耐
心太軟流水ok~
黃寶蘋果批唔算太甜～
菠蘿沙冰嘅菠蘿就太酸～
整體不過不失～
千層酥入口都夠鬆化～
I loved my dessert! It seemed thoughtfully made and presented, and was worth the wait. This place is often busy with a wait, especially on the weekends. But definitely worth a try.
